| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1501 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 836c9080-4fb4-5189-a344-9850e45f23fe"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
